com.b2international.snowowl.core.date

Class EffectiveTimes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.core.date.EffectiveTimes

  • public abstract class EffectiveTimes
extends java.lang.Object
    Effective Times should be always in GMT time. Use this class when working with effective times in any ontology, this will ensure the proper parsing and formatting of them.
    Since:
    3.9
